Title: Fix missing graphs in notifications
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: notifications
Date: 1648198479
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p23

Since version 2.0.0, quotes are allowed in service descriptions.
If a notification was triggered for such service, the graphs were missing.

Furthermore, the mail subject showed "&quot" instead of quotes.
